HEADWORD: nonpartisanship
<hw>nonpartisanship</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An inclination to weigh both
views or opinions equally; absence of bias toward any particular
party.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> impartiality.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

